#: ../../manual/render/lighting/lamps/spot.rst:28
msgid "Shadows"
msgstr "阴影"

#: ../../manual/render/lighting/lamps/spot.rst:34
msgid "Spot Shape"
msgstr "聚光灯形状"

#: ../../manual/render/lighting/lamps/spot.rst:39
msgid ""
"Changing the Spot options also changes the appearance of the spotlight as "
"displayed in the 3D View."
msgstr "更改此选项会更改3D视图中显示的聚光灯外观。"

#: ../../manual/render/lighting/lamps/spot.rst:54
msgid "Size"
msgstr "尺寸"

#: ../../manual/render/lighting/lamps/spot.rst:42
msgid ""
"The size of the outer cone of a *Spot*, which largely controls the circular "
"area a *Spot* light covers. This slider in fact controls the angle at the top "
"of the lighting cone, and can be between (1.0 to 180.0)."
msgstr ""
"*Spot* 外锥的大小，主要控制 *Spot* 光线覆盖的圆形区域。实际上，此滑块控制顶部"
"灯光圆锥的角度，可以在（1.0到180.0）之间。"

#: ../../manual/render/lighting/lamps/spot.rst:47
msgid "Changing the spot *Size* option."
msgstr "更改聚光灯 *SIZE* 选项。"

#: ../../manual/render/lighting/lamps/spot.rst:83
msgid "Blend"
msgstr "混合"

#: ../../manual/render/lighting/lamps/spot.rst:57
msgid ""
"The *Blend* slider controls the inner cone of the *Spot*. The *Blend* value "
"can be between (0.0 to 1.0). The value is proportional and represents that "
"amount of space that the inner cone should occupy inside the outer cone "
"*Size*."
msgstr ""
"*Blend* 滑块控制 *Spot* 的内锥。 *Blend* 值可以在（0.0到1.0）之间。该值是成比"
"例的，表示内锥体应在外锥体内占据的空间量 *尺寸*。"

#: ../../manual/render/lighting/lamps/spot.rst:62
msgid ""
"The inner cone boundary line indicates the point at which light from the "
"*Spot* will start to blur/soften; before this point its light will mostly be "
"full strength. The larger the value of *Blend* the more blurred/soft the "
"edges of the spotlight will be, and the smaller the inner cone's circular "
"area will be (as it starts to blur/soften earlier)."
msgstr ""
"内锥边界线表示来自 *Spot* 的光开始模糊/柔化的点; 在此之前它的光线将大部分是全"
"强度。 *Blend* 的值越大，聚光灯的边缘越模糊/柔和，内锥体的圆形区域越小（因为它"
"开始模糊/柔化更早）。"

#: ../../manual/render/lighting/lamps/spot.rst:67
msgid ""
"To make the *Spot* have a sharper falloff rate and therefore less blurred/"
"soft edges, decrease the value of *Blend*. Setting *Blend* to 0.0 results in "
"very sharp spotlight edges, without any transition between light and shadow."
msgstr ""
"要使 *Spot* 具有更锐利的衰减率并因此减少模糊/柔和边缘，请减小 *Blend* 的值。"
"将 *Blend* 设置为0.0会产生非常清晰的聚光灯边缘，光线和阴影之间没有任何过渡。"

#: ../../manual/render/lighting/lamps/spot.rst:71
msgid ""
"The falloff rate of the *Spot* lamp light is a ratio between the *Blend* and "
"*Size* values; the larger the circular gap between the two, the more gradual "
"the light fades between *Blend* and *Size*."
msgstr ""
"*Spot* 灯光的衰减率是 *Blend* 和 *Size* 值之间的比率; 当两者之间的圆形间隙变"
"大，*Blend* 和 *Size* 之间的光线逐渐消失。"

#: ../../manual/render/lighting/lamps/spot.rst:74
msgid ""
"*Blend* and *Size* only control the *Spot* light cone's aperture and softness "
"(\"radial\" falloff); they do not control the shadow's softness as shown "
"below."
msgstr ""
"*Blend* 和 *Size* 仅控制 *Spot* 光锥的光圈和柔和度（“径向”衰减）;它们不能控制"
"如下所示阴影的柔和度。"

#: ../../manual/render/lighting/lamps/spot.rst:80
msgid ""
"Render showing the soft edge spotlighted area and the sharp/hard object "
"shadow."
msgstr "渲染显示柔化边缘聚光区域和锐利/硬物体阴影。"

#: ../../manual/render/lighting/lamps/spot.rst:82
msgid ""
"Notice in the picture above that the object's shadow is sharp as a result of "
"the ray tracing, whereas the spotlight edges are soft. If you want other "
"items to cast soft shadows within the *Spot* area, you will need to alter "
"other shadow settings."
msgstr ""
"请注意，在上图中，由于光线跟踪，物体的阴影很清晰，而聚光灯边缘是柔和的。如果你"
"希望其他项目在 *Spot* 区域内投射柔和阴影，则需要更改其他阴影设置。"

